snippet: The 22-year-old woman was said to have jumped to her death at a mall after being raped by private security guards there.
abstract: Hundreds of Chinese police officers in riot gear are deployed into streets surrounding shopping mall in southern Beijing to contain large protest that was ignited by death of 22-year-old woman rumored to have been raped by security guards.
lead_paragraph: The 22-year-old woman was said to have jumped to her death at a mall after being raped by private security guards there.

headline.seo: Police Quell Protest in Beijing Over Woman’s Death
headline.main: Police Quell Protest in Beijing Over Woman’s Death
headline.print_headline: China: Police Contain Protest Aimed At Worker’s Death and Rumor of Rape
